{"id": 573, "genre": 1001, "title": "拍照不上相是一种怎样的体验？", "description": "接受现实吧盆宇，其实你就长那样。", "record_count": 7897, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194240N7JsH3nMR2aKwQZ1.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-17T01:01:05Z", "options": [{"id": 19201, "content": "别人眼里的我是不是也这么丑？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263377}, {"id": 17922, "content": "拍别人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256164}, {"id": 17923, "content": "朋友圈里只发风景照", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147506}, {"id": 18179, "content": "及其厌恶拍照", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258026}, {"id": 21764, "content": "把手机自拍镜头贴上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281462}, {"id": 18181, "content": "就是丑好嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258035}, {"id": 19205, "content": "接受现实，不照相", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263404}, {"id": 44037, "content": "丑哭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 440413}, {"id": 17926, "content": "去照相馆照相。照相师傅照完一次。说 再照一边。照完一次说 再照一边 照完再照", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256223}, {"id": 23046, "content": "一个朋友自拍就想挡着脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 288470}, {"id": 17671, "content": "“你照片好丑啊！”\n看看脸\n“拍照技术不错啊！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 60, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254951}, {"id": 17672, "content": "害怕被任何镜头对着", "image": null, "praise_count": 1280, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124359}, {"id": 17673, "content": "相亲被接受总是有一句\n“她本人比照片漂亮，见见再说。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254951}, {"id": 17929, "content": "反正我不用自己照片当头像  从来没有  估计以后也不会有", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256250}, {"id": 17674, "content": "已经接受现实 /再见", "image": null, "praise_count": 671, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 98651}, {"id": 18442, "content": "有人和我一样不上相，这样我就舒服多了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259101}, {"id": 17675, "content": "相亲被介绍总是加一句\n“她本人比照片漂亮，见见再说。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 88, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254951}, {"id": 17931, "content": "不知道自己真正长什么样，不知道别人眼里自己什么样。?不会就是照片那个样吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 230687}, {"id": 17677, "content": "每次打照片，总有人评论大脸！", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181259}, {"id": 17678, "content": "出去玩可以认真专注地拍风景", "image": null, "praise_count": 1206, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248086}, {"id": 17934, "content": "不是说好斜角45度吗！骗人！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 208374}, {"id": 17935, "content": "并不知道自己到底长啥样", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212968}, {"id": 17680, "content": "要有自知之明", "image": null, "praise_count": 263, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255075}, {"id": 26384, "content": "别闹了，根本没有不上相，就是丑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311407}, {"id": 21777, "content": "其实是真的越长越丑了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281554}, {"id": 17682, "content": "面基经常听到说：“你比照片帅啊……”……有好多基友因为我不上相把我在面基之前就pass掉，因此少泡到好多帅比……", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 220678}, {"id": 18450, "content": "只接受全身照 从来不会自拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259168}, {"id": 18964, "content": "最害怕出现在我妈的相机里并且她一直觉得把我拍的很美于是我经常出没于她的朋友圈。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262096}, {"id": 21268, "content": "很煞心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269004}, {"id": 17685, "content": "嘻嘻，我就是风景", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004648teOgLbjZocKYsH40.jpg", "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197390}, {"id": 17686, "content": "重没有去想这问题！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232946}, {"id": 17942, "content": "只能用特效相机 并且还得没脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256320}, {"id": 17687, "content": "相册里都是别人的照片 风景照", "image": null, "praise_count": 460, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164732}, {"id": 17944, "content": "学会了如何找角度?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256326}, {"id": 23064, "content": "对不起我上相", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290286}, {"id": 18457, "content": "360度多方位全死角", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248583}, {"id": 18969, "content": "不上相的拍照永远只有一个角度?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252204}, {"id": 17690, "content": "总会说“我不喜欢照相”然而没人时又努力自拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 959, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 222564}, {"id": 17946, "content": "拍个照跟玩捉迷藏一样，东躲躲西藏藏，最后拍了一张照连亲妈都不认得", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246901}, {"id": 17692, "content": "剪完头发拍照只拍头发不忍心拍脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253323}, {"id": 18460, "content": "怎么p都觉得少点什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259241}, {"id": 17949, "content": "小时候怕拍照，拍出来没有哥哥好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256448}, {"id": 19229, "content": "还不如不照", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263463}, {"id": 17950, "content": "害怕女朋友发相片的时候，以为我是个富二代", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256457}, {"id": 18718, "content": "丧失了对拍照的兴趣，拍完自己都不想看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260491}, {"id": 19230, "content": "我去，这是我吗？丑逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263459}, {"id": 17695, "content": "已成好友中风靡的表情包", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239783}, {"id": 17696, "content": "丑就丑啊！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232788}, {"id": 17952, "content": "不想面对镜头，一拍照就觉得像上刑场。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256433}, {"id": 18720, "content": "猪八戒照镜子，里外不是人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260543}]}